          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "可恨那秦嬴政昏荒无道，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "他本是西戎种混乱中朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "变封建为郡县起祸根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "把人民当奴隶滥逞英豪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "阿房宫三百里内藏娇娆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "若民间有私钱性命难逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "天命当保，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "他还想成神仙快乐逍遥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "空怀着报仇志昼夜心焦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "到如今还不见草泽英豪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只苦了众百姓受尽煎熬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我想把专制君万剐千刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恨不能学专诸刺杀王僚！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人内嚷。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众人 （内同白） 秦皇帝来到，还不早躲么！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张良作惊。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "猛听得众百姓纷纷嚷道，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "待鄙人走向前细问根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "诸位请了！所嚷何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众人 （内同白） 秦皇帝有东游泰山，昨日路过阳武，就此驻驿了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张良作惊喜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我正想锄刈此贼，无法可施。不料他竟自先来送死，真令我好欢喜也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我正想起义兵诛锄无道，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "谁料他入罗网插翅难逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "替祖国报公仇就在今朝！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张良走。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是苍海公家，不免上前叩门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张良叩门。苍海公装带锥上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼中黑白要分明，天谴魔君杀不平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "外面和人叩门？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是张良。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（苍海公作开门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是子房兄！请里面谈话。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张良、苍海公同入。苍海公关门。张良、苍海公分坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苍海公，"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "子房兄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我已打听明白，那暴君是从博浪沙经过，请公就在此地行事如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "子房兄见教极是，但是子房兄须要躲避才是。呵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "尊一声张公子且宽怀抱，"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你赶紧整行装先事奔逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "且免得事不成贻累英豪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张良执苍海公手，作起立。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "尊一声苍海公你见识太小，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自古道共患难与子同袍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我与你早已订生死之交。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你心中休得要自寻烦恼"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公子差矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你心中休得要自寻烦恼"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我非是将公子有心取笑，"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我要想留一个恢复根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为怎的要同去枉死一遭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "要知道我此去凶多吉少"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，即当遵命了！苍海公在上，受我一拜！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我也有一拜！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "苍海公在尘埃将身拜倒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "生辞别张子房盖世英豪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张良起立执手。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倘若是我此去事机不妙，"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "逃走了这魔道世外逍遥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "莫把这弥天恨抛在九霄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "还望你施妙计将仇来报"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "勇士前往，但请放心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还望你施妙计将仇来报"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "秦始皇灭六国冤仇非小，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为天下除此贼天日昭昭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我死在九泉下万劫难逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我若是昧良心忍辱不报"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既是如此，公子就请起程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张良更衣。家院上，牵马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张良揖别。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "辞别了苍海公把路行！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张良上马，哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "子房好男子，为何作此儿女之态？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "等候了苍海公成就大功！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张良催马，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听一声秦嬴政位离大宝，"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我这里霎时间怨气都消。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "扰害得众百姓痛哭嚎啕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "今日里要在我锥下……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（苍海公观锥。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "狗命难逃！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（苍海公收铁锥，下。）"
        }
      ],
