      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四太监、四御林军上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咦咦咦咦！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秦始皇戴王帽、穿黄龙蟒袍上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "竹帛烟消，兵气销。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秦始皇坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "法律由专断，威权种祸胎。生不访家贼，死上断头台。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朕，秦始皇。因前日百姓不服，私下议论纷纷，所以朕特颁一条极严法律：倘"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若有人，私下议论，立刻问斩，以免后患。又观东南王气正盛，所以命驾东巡，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "察看那里的民情，这正是为君的难啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "百姓们不知是朕即国家，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "朕立意除净那民党萌芽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又何怕有刺客在博浪沙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！话虽如此，但是古人说得好，有备无患，方是这个主意呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫一声内侍臣，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "有爪牙和心腹护卫孤家"
        },
        {
          "character": "太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "安排副车，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "张姓冠李姓戴莫要喧哗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
