    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "二御林军",
        "众人",
        "御林军",
        "秦始皇",
        "苍海公"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四太监引秦始皇上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "若非巧计安排定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "已作黄泉新鬼魂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秦始皇里位坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二御林军同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二御林军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启奏万岁：刺客拿住了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "绑上来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "二御林军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "绑上殿来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众人 （内同白） 吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二御林军押苍海公背绑上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "悲哉秦人真虎狼，"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "欺侮六国囚侯王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "但恨不见秦先亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二御林军同跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二御林军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刺客解到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大胆刺客，你受何人主使，胆敢前来行刺？从实招来，免你一死。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔这暴君，人人想食尔肉！我为民除害，有何人主使？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苍海公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有也不向尔说！你杀我一人，也难安安稳稳，长保你金銮殿上这把金交椅！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秦始皇气。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好毒骂吓！啊哈，好毒骂吓！御林军与朕剁作肉泥骨酱！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（御林军拔刀，苍海公撞柱自死。御林军收刀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "御林军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刺客死了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦始皇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斩草除根，方免后患！哪，呵哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
