          "text": "（张良急上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻得苍海公已死，暴君命人各处搜杀主使之人，这、这、这、这便如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张良低头想。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈有了！我有故人项伯，在下邳居住，不免到他家中躲避便了！唉！苍海公"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵！我误尔的命了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张良向空拜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众人 （内同白） 起驾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这暴、暴、暴、暴……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众人 （内同白） 嘎！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张良慌忙逃下。）"
        }
      ],
